    {
      "id": "347de824-cd00-49c5-afb1-2bbfe3e68878",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Giving effective feedback and monitoring its effects in an harduous task. Thus, in order to understand the effectiveness of feedback, the authors compare the behaviors and learning performance of two groups of students: ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "347de824-cd00-49c5-afb1-2bbfe3e68878",
        "parent": {
