    {
      "id": "38b496ca-170a-445e-8349-328eddcd5758",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Samples uses 49 undergraduates. Differences in learning performance were assessed using t-test and ANCOVA. Diffferences in behavioral features were evaluated with lag sequential analysis and Hidden Marov Chains. ",
