    {
      "id": "66e0d424-7d3b-4527-89b5-b06ad989464f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that students who received feedback tended to be more engaged than the control group → e.g. they completed more elearning assignments. Moreover, the analysis showed that, while all students used all LMS systems, students in experimental group were more active in task and discussion views and posts, updates on tasks and group performance viewing. Moreover, all students tended to increase their engagement as the semester advanced, but the increase was more noticeable in the experimental group.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "66e0d424-7d3b-4527-89b5-b06ad989464f",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
